data.description: Look no farther "Powdersville, popular sought after school system".  Homes don't come on the market that often for larger families.  4BR/3BA sits in a central location just minutes from Easley, Greenville, or Anderson; your choice of commute.  The large corner lot, in a well-known mature wooded subdivision, has curb appeal, and spacious parking; with an up-to-date newly installed landscaper's dream irrigation system.  It has a fenced backyard perfect for a dog walk, an attached garage.  Inside boasts a spacious living area with updated fireplace/hearth, an open kitchen with pantry.  MBR-on main level has en-suite BA w/platform soaker tub.  Upstairs has 2 massive BR's and 1 small BR.  Come see today-in Sitton Hill Subdivision.
